The paper deals with the problem of quantifying the Pareto optimal boundary in the achievable rate region over MISO interference channels, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also proposes two new distributed optimal beamforming algorithms, which are related to control systems (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.MM). Finally, the paper establishes convergence proofs for both algorithms, which is related to theoretical computer science (cs.LG).
